Sentencas: Aiming to offer a high-performance Co-free cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs), a series of La0.8Sr0.2Fe1-xCuxO3-delta (LSFCux, x = 0.0-0.3) nanofiber cathodes were synthesized by the electrospinning method.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of fibrous La0.8Sr0.2Fe1-xCuxO3-d cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The effects of various Cu doping amounts on the crystal structure, fiber morphology, and electrochemical performance of LSF nanofiber cathode materials were investigated.
